{"tid":2035983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不如聽日唔好搞咁多野啦","createTime":"2020-05-26T08:05:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T13:24:11.000Z","uid":229095,"like":39,"dislike":58,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"f8f7cfbab06df7c04aeb1499f35aef9089a328e5","tid":2035983,"uid":229095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T08:05:19.000Z","msg":"比你圍到立會又點撚樣啊<br />\n人地過幾日又審過啦<br />\n你係咪可以日日圍啊？<br />\n而家講緊出一次就拉百個告暴動啊<br />\n你搞革命係為過程嘅你咪出去送頭囉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D6va8uX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD6va8uX.jpg&h=b7c93f09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n已經foresee聽日會全軍覆沒<br />\n叫人衝個班撚樣全撚部都係自己唔會衝<br />\n叫人全民勇武自己就係屋企嘆冷氣食西瓜<br />\n一味係到吹風話拉到都告唔快<br />\n事實上就係個個都冇希望要認罪"},{"pid":"62d64e6ba494b6ab67d8e43f122be31e49e073ba","tid":2035983,"uid":8833,"like":5,"dislike":10,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T08:06:12.000Z","msg":"樓下<br />\n直接block<br />\n唔洗覆"},{"pid":"da3835a98335ab061a28f920df70d4477bed9503","tid":2035983,"uid":17732,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T08:08:00.000Z","msg":"我建議自己罷工<br />\n唔好理有冇用，個個唔行第一步，永遠唔會去到大罷工<br />\n之後係屋企柒一日"},{"pid":"4152bace8cabcc349394034c009c13cecfcc71e9","tid":2035983,"uid":3357,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T08:13:29.000Z","msg":"黎明行動 金鐘相見<br />\n全民駕駛 以車代鐵<br />\n路面要車 地面要人<br />\n527塞爆港島<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ce1c57ba39bfa204841c651994b32118c20d091","tid":2035983,"uid":77143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T08:14:06.000Z","msg":"登陸諾曼第"},{"pid":"5b2fee11ca76d94da58ddb81c116dc6ddb6beaa0","tid":2035983,"uid":324084,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T08:14:44.000Z","msg":"block撚左"},{"pid":"a0a00b65512fed6bef48c15d37090c184